snippet.textDisplay:
One Million views finally!Though  Very less than what this song deserves!
I have gone crazy for this song! Really love the feel which this song takes through. Jazz, Blues in an old song! Truely Amazing!

This was the first time I noticed Sara Haider. After this song, I have gone through every song of Season 7 & 8 only to hear her Backing Vocals! She is truly Amazing!! :D

Ali Zafar's voice directly touches my heart. I don't know why, but his voice keeps resonating within me till hours of hearing this song. He is superb! 

Omran Sahfique, loved your guitar solo at 3:17

Haidar Ali, lovely piano tunes and pieces and chords playing in the background throughout the song are amazing. Just loved them.


WOW!! I don't know the name of the gentleman who is the bassist but i get carried away each and every time whenever camera is being focused on him, sitting posture, style is outstanding....KUDOS to all the Houseband Members... I watch Coke Studio Pakistan because of them and the variation of music and fusion they come up with. :) <3

Strings, I salute you for bringing this song to this season.
